{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Meklejeet to KUNGA wiſ- fi juhs Behdigt eekſch tahs Sem- mes/ kas winna Teefu padarra/ meklejeet Taifnibu/ meklejeet Lehnprahtibu/ jaſchu juhs tap- feet apſlehptt tai Deena tahs Bahrsibas ta KUNGA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo Gaza taps atſtahta/ un Aſkalons par pohſtu Weetu/ Asdoda taps Deenas-Widdû atſdsihta/ un Ekrong taps iſ- faknohts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wajteem! kas garx Juhe- ru dſihwo/ tai Tautai Kreeti/ ta KUNGA Wahrdg nahks pahr jums/ ak Kanaans tu Wi- liſteru Semune! un es gribbu terwi nomaitaht/ ka tur Eedſih- wotajt wairs ne buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Teefa garx Juhen buhs par Buhdahm/ iſraktahtm Akkahm to Gannu un Awju Laidareem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta patti Walsta buhs preekſch teem Atliffuscheem ta Namma Juhda/ ka tee tur eek- cha ganna. Walkardôs tee ap- guldiſees Aſkalona Natmunds/ kad tas KUNGS winnu Deews tohs peemeklehs/ un winno Zee- unnju buhs atgreeſis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es eſnu Moaba Mehdi- chanur dſirdejs/ un to Lanma- chann to Behrnu Amnon/ ar ko ee, mannus Laudis irr mehdij- cht/ un irr leelijſchees prett win- ai Robbeschahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht/ tik teefcham ka es\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "dsihwoju/ faeka tas KUNGS Zebaoſ/ tas Ifraeta Deeus: Moabs buhs ka Sodoma/ un Ammona Behrni ka Gomorra/ weens Nahtru Kruhns/ un Sahls Bedre/ un weena pohſta Weeta muhſchigi. Manni at- likkuſchi Laudis tohs aplaupihs/ un tee Atlizzinatee no manneem Laudim tohs eemantohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas notiks winneem par winno Lepnibu/ jo tee irr meh- diſcht/ un leelijſchees prett teem Laudim ta KUNGA Zebaoſ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS buhs bree- migs prett winneem/ jo winſch tedeldehs wiſſus Deewus tahs Semmes/ un ikweens no fawas Weetas winnu peeſuhgs/ wiſſas Sallas to Pagaxu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir juhs Mohru Landis tapfeet zaur mannu Sohbinu nokauti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir winſch isſteepe farut Rohku prekt Seemelt/ un no- maiaths Affurn. Un darrihs Nintivt par pohſtu Weetu/ tik fanfu ka iveenu Tuſfneſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnas Widdû ap- gulſees tee gannami Bulki/ wiſſi Swehri to Pagaxu/ ir tas Dumpig/ un tas Efis mahjoſs winnu Granata Dahrsds/ win- nu Balkine dſeedahs eekſch Loh- geem/ un tee Kraukti us teem Sleekſneem/ jo tee Zeedra Galoi taps nopſehſti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schis irr tas Pileſahte/ kas ta preezajahs/ kas drohſchi dſihwo/ kas tawa Strdi faeka:\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
